  "contentHtml": "\n    \n    \n        \n                <ul>\n                    \n                     <li><a href=\"/news/diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Diagnostics</a></li>                     <li>1 min read</li>                 </ul>\n                            \n        \n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Mar 20, 2026 at 12:18 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><a href=\"/tag/gwalior\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gwalior</a>: <a href=\"/tag/thyrocare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Thyrocare</a> Technologies Limited is sharpening its focus on tier-2 and tier-3 markets with the launch of its first <a href=\"/tag/diagnostic+laboratory\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">diagnostic laboratory</a> in <a href=\"/tag/gwalior\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gwalior</a>, in partnership with Excellence Diagnostics, as the diagnostics major looks to tap rising demand beyond metro cities.With this move, the company expands its footprint in <a href=\"/tag/madhya+pradesh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Madhya Pradesh</a> to three laboratories, adding to its presence in Bhopal and Indore, positioning itself to capture growing demand for affordable and reliable diagnostic services in central India.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->The newly launched laboratory is equipped with advanced testing infrastructure and supported by trained professionals, enabling accurate and timely diagnostic results. It is designed to cater to both routine and specialised testing needs, supporting preventive as well as ongoing healthcare requirements.\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        The expansion aligns with Thyrocare’s strategy to strengthen its network and address the growing demand for reliable diagnostic services in emerging markets, particularly beyond metro cities.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->Commenting on the launch, Rahul Guha, MD and CEO, Thyrocare, said, “Our focus is on making high-quality and reliable diagnostic services accessible to every Indian household. This new facility reflects our continued efforts to expand our presence while addressing diagnostic gaps through a technology-led and patient-focused approach.”With this launch, Thyrocare continues to deepen its presence in <a href=\"/tag/madhya+pradesh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Madhya Pradesh</a>, focusing on expanding access to diagnostic services across non-metro cities and strengthening its nationwide network.                    \n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Mar 20, 2026 at 12:18 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Mar 20, 2026 at 12:18 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                           